        <lg type="poem">
          <head>1L: Luri treckt de Abendluch</head>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Luri treckt de Abendluch</l>
            <l>Æwert Feld so glind;</l>
            <l>Wenn'k mi nu wat wünschen much,</l>
            <l>Weer'k noch eenmal Kind.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Lisen weiht ęr Lust un Larm</l>
            <l>Wit hendal na't Moor,</l>
            <l>As Musik, so week un warm,</l>
            <l>All as weer't en Chor.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Kumt mi nich min Lęben vœr</l>
            <l>As en swaren Drom?</l>
            <l>Wak ik so mal op as Gœr</l>
            <l>Abends ünnern Bom!</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>All min Freid is sünner Klang,</l>
            <l>Un min Hart is arm,</l>
            <l>Hör'k in Srhummern as Gesang</l>
            <l>So de Kinner larm';</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Sackt mi rein de Spaden dal</l>
            <l>Ut de sware Hand.</l>
            <l>Gravt </l>
            <l>Rin int Kinnerland?</l>
          </lg>
